{"tid":391349,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人晚晚發惡夢，訓醒都會記得好清楚？","createTime":"2017-09-07T16:52:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-08T19:14:13.000Z","uid":3206,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0f0f42d12221a9b29ec9056b6f993fb269d9e97a","tid":391349,"uid":3206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T16:52:35.000Z","msg":"其實應該點解決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n又唔係話日日都惡夢咁誇，但一定係負面既<br />\n每朝都會記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n從來無發過好夢<br />\n<br />\n又唔係壓力大丫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n持續左好多年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無論係讀書，升左asso每日玩住過，畢業做廢青，返廢工，去長旅行 都係一直發惡夢<br />\n<br />\n俾人拮愛滋針 仆街 追殺 跳崖 返工奶大野 朋友死左 自己有絕症 海嘯 老竇想姦我家姐 九唔搭八既mix埋 乜撚都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n人地話記得啲夢<br />\n即係淺眠<br />\n所以訓幾多都會攰<br />\n我正正就係咁 返工訓八個鐘都唔夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6133b269b8826b0bd8dbea7f7133939334406ccd","tid":391349,"uid":52068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T16:54:43.000Z","msg":"有冇做運動"},{"pid":"c953cdcd671f56cefdd881cee4352b06842888f4","tid":391349,"uid":3206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T17:19:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇做運動</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無呀<br />\n之前試過一星期跑三次 維持左一個月左右<br />\n好似都冇咩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />